### 5. Your Rights

#### Under **GDPR**, you have the right to:
- Access, correct, or delete your personal data  
- Object to or restrict processing  
- Data portability  
- Withdraw consent at any time

#### Under **CCPA/CPRA**, California residents have the right to:
- Know what personal data we collect  
- Request deletion of personal data  
- Opt out of the sale or sharing of personal data  
- Non-discrimination for exercising privacy rights

#### Under **CalOPPA**, we disclose:
- Our privacy policy is linked within the app  
- Users can contact us via the FAQ and Contact page  
- We honor Do Not Track signals (when implemented)

